author: Lego_fan_
title: Neat part collection
review: I have Recently picked up the Walmart edition of this set and have really gotten into creating my own creations. I love building cars, Planes, and spaceships.  I find that classic sets are great for basic parts. But this one is really good for It comes with a nice tire collection and other parts for building cars. I think that anybody who finds it at a good price should pick one up because I have spent 48 hours playing with this set over the weekend. I would highly suggest this set to any Lego classic fans, or fans who like creating.
